Export data to CSV.

Track renewal dates.

10. Conclusion
The Basic Subscription Manager successfully demonstrates fundamental Python programming concepts while providing a practical tool for managing monthly expenses. Its simplicity makes it accessible to beginners, while its extensibility offers opportunities for future development. This project highlights the importance of input validation, error handling, and user-friendly design in software development.

